--color-grind-text: #f5f0e8;
--color-grind-muted: #6b6560;
--color-grind-border: rgba(200, 169, 126, 0.15);
--color-grind-page: #F8F8F8;
```

## Getting Started

```bash
git clone https://github.com/lianxxxx/offline-practice
cd offline-practice

composer install
npm install

cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate

php artisan serve
npm run dev
```

## Mail Setup

The contact form uses Laravel Mail. Configure your `.env`:

```env
MAIL_MAILER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=your-mail-host
MAIL_PORT=587
MAIL_USERNAME=your-username
MAIL_PASSWORD=your-password
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=hello@grindcoffee.ph
MAIL_FROM_NAME="Grind"
```

